"},{"id":"457169","title":"Aditya Birla Digital Fashion Ventures Ltd invested in Wrogn, acquiring 2.53% for INR 6.57 Cr and INR 35.81 Cr via OCRPS.\nWrogn, a fashion brand, reported FY25 revenue of INR 223.23 Cr. The acquisition expands ABDFVL's digital-first brand portfolio.","summary":"Aditya Birla Digital Fashion Ventures Ltd invested in Wrogn, acquiring 2.53% for INR 6.57 Cr and INR 35.81 Cr via OCRPS.\nWrogn, a fashion brand, reported FY25 revenue of INR 223.23 Cr. The acquisition expands ABDFVL's digital-first brand portfolio.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.aspx?Pname=f16026c8-1dea-4cdf-99b2-eedddd88429b.pdf","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-28T18:23:18","source":"BSE"},{"id":"801748272026974848","title":"Aditya Birla Fashion faces Rs 217 lakh demand from customs over IGST dispute.\nThe company plans to legally contest the demand order at CESTAT.","summary":"Aditya Birla Fashion faces Rs 217 lakh demand from customs over IGST dispute.\nThe company plans to legally contest the demand order at CESTAT.","url":"https://sqst.in/Z0jBk","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-21T15:11:23","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"801298019446657664","title":"Aditya Birla Fashion shares fell 8% after equity deals worth ₹289 crore.","summary":"Aditya Birla Fashion shares fell 8% after equity deals worth ₹289 crore.","url":"https://sqst.in/shareMessage?msgId=801298019446657633","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-20T09:22:15","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"445625","title":"Aditya Birla Fashion plans to sell 3% stake via block deal worth $32M.\nThe deal starts at ₹65.78/share, 8.5% below current market price.","summary":"Aditya Birla Fashion plans to sell 3% stake via block deal worth $32M.\nThe deal starts at ₹65.78/share, 8.5% below current market price.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-19T20:29:02","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"796978878741266176","title":"Aditya Birla Fashion & Retail's Q3 retail segment grew 46% YoY; consolidated revenue rose 35.6%.\neCommerce operations increased 138% YoY, contributing 5.1% of total revenue.","summary":"Aditya Birla Fashion & Retail's Q3 retail segment grew 46% YoY; consolidated revenue rose 35.6%.\neCommerce operations increased 138% YoY, contributing 5.1% of total revenue.","url":"https://sqst.in/shareMessage?msgId=796978878741266199","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-08T11:19:31","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"794186394948032512","title":"Aditya Birla Fashion faces a tax demand of ₹132.9 crore from Haryana tax authority.\nThe company denies charges, plans to appeal against the demand order.","summary":"Aditya Birla Fashion faces a tax demand of ₹132.9 crore from Haryana tax authority.\nThe company denies charges, plans to appeal against the demand order.","url":"https://sqst.in/xPtSb","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2025-12-31T18:23:11","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"422641","title":"Pilani Investment acquired 2.44 crore shares of Aditya Birla Fashion.\nThe purchases occurred in the open market between Dec 23-29.","summary":"Pilani Investment acquired 2.44 crore shares of Aditya Birla Fashion.\nThe purchases occurred in the open market between Dec 23-29.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2025-12-31T12:41:22","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"789448088214312960","title":"Aditya Birla Fashion faced a tax demand of ₹13.8 crore over input tax credit mismatch.\nThe company plans to appeal, stating no current financial or operational impact.","summary":"Aditya Birla Fashion faced a tax demand of ₹13.8 crore over input tax credit mismatch.\nThe company plans to appeal, stating no current financial or operational impact.","url":"https://sqst.in/NyaP4","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2025-12-18T16:34:51","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"785816351165576704","title":"CGST Chandigarh issued a tax demand of ₹1.49 Cr with ₹13,715 interest and ₹14.9 Cr penalty to Aditya Birla Fashion.\nThe dispute involves excess input tax credit due to vendor default; the company plans to appeal, deeming it invalid."